data.description: Conveniently located, this spacious home featuring 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, double pane windows and a large 0.85 acre lot was updated with a new roof, new appliances, and new HVAC in 2021. There is also a large bonus room that can be used as either a second living, office space or a 4th bedroom. It is only 5 minutes from Connally schools, 6 minutes from TSTC, and 15 minutes to both downtown Waco and Baylor. The quick access to I35 also allows you to reach the DFW Metroplex in only 1.5 hours.
